headline.print_headline: European Banks Raise More Capital Before ECB Stress Test: Report
headline.main: European Banks Raise More Capital Before ECB Stress Test: Report

lead_paragraph: Euro zone banks have raised 35 percent more capital ahead of the European Central Bank's (ECB) latest stress test than they had set aside before the 2011 review, according to a report published by law firm Linklaters.
